====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[send]]; to [[deliver]]; to [[present]]
#: {{zh-co|致辭|to deliver a speech}}
# to [[express]]; to [[convey]]
#: {{zh-co|致以|to express; to extend}}
# to [[cause]]; to [[incur]]
#: {{zh-co|致癌|to '''cause''' cancer}}
# to [[devote]]; to [[exhaust]]; to [[use up]] {{gl|one's energy, efforts, etc.}}
#: {{zh-co|致力|to concentrate on; to devote oneself to}}
# to [[achieve]]; to [[attain]]
#: {{zh-co|致富|to get rich; to achieve wealth}}
#: {{zh-co|致知|to attain knowledge}}
# [[engaging]] [[style]]; [[manner]] or style that [[engage]]s [[attention]] or [[arouse]]s [[interest]]
#: {{zh-co|有致|interesting; appealing}}
#: {{zh-co|興致|interest; mood to enjoy}}
# to [[result]] in; [[so that]]
#: {{zh-co|以致|resulting in; so that}}
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to [[contract]] {{gl|an illness}}
#: {{zh-co|致 著[着] 病{pīⁿ}|to contract an illness|MN}}
